\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I'll emit a disabling frequency the moment anything goes sideways. You won't hear a thing, but the Tourists will be incapacitated.}
