\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Zoom in.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I did. It was a small brownish green blob, and now it's a bigger one.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 RICHARD}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Keep going.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OK, now I see the blob is actually three smaller blobs.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 RICHARD}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Keep going.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2880\ri2160\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 (sigh)}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 OK, now I see some blue spots in the brown blobs. Wait, there's way more detail in here.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron keeps zooming in as the other watch him. The blue dots reveal gray spots on the edges. The gray spots have long dark lines reaching other gray dots. The gray dots have many square criss-crossing lines... They're cities.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Oh my god...}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron looks up over the monitor at the tiny fleck of brownish green on the wall where the laser is pointing. He looks back down at the sprawling city on the side of a giant lake. He looks back up at the far wall, where the entire continent blends in with it's neighbors. He slowly picks a new location and zooms into a volcanic mountain range where a gray speck rises from the blue.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 RICHARD}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Pretty cool, huh?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 This is... what is this?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AMY}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You're not on Earth, Aaron. }
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CAPTAIN WHEELER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Oh come on! Did you really think you were on Earth this whole time?}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AARON}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 I have no idea where I am! I was taken from a dock in Chicago to what I thought was an island. When I woke up, I was being charged with some heinous crime I still don't understand. I think they'd have killed me for it, but somehow I ended up here instead. I still don't know where "here" is!}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 AMY}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 It's the World, Aaron. There isn't another name for it because the people here have never known anything else. There is no astronomy, no solar system to analyze here. You're standing where the Sun is. The walls of this room represent a shell that completely surrounds it, about 95 million miles away from the center. That shell is our World. We live inside it.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Aaron contemplates her statement for a moment before his knees buckle and he drops to the floor in a seated position.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 RICHARD}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Woah there, big guy.}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Richard helps him rest against the glass walled railing.}
\par\pard\plain \li3600\ri-360\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 CAPTAIN WHEELER}
\par\pard\plain \li2160\ri1440\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Enough of the science lesson bullshit. Where is the device, Amy?}
\par\pard\plain \li720\ri-720\sb240\sl-240\slmult0\ql\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Amy steps up to the view pointer and takes a look around to get her bearing. After a moment chooses a place in the mountain range past Split Rock City. Something that seems reasonable for their arrival nearby.}
